RentAmount(oliveGarden, 2000).
Fluffy(fluffy).
Tom(tom).

∀x (ManagedBuilding(x) → DepositRequired(x)).
∀b (Rent(tom, b) → ManagedBuilding(b)).

∀x (ManagedBuilding(x) ∧ AllowedPet(x, y)).
